@{
    Layout = null;
}

<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>
<head>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>Page produit détaillé</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.2.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-GJzZqFGwb1QTTN6wy59ffF1BuGJpLSa9DkKMp0DgiMDm4iYMj70gZWKYbI706tWS" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.6.3/css/all.css" integrity="sha384-UHRtZLI+pbxtHCWp1t77Bi1L4ZtiqrqD80Kn4Z8NTSRyMA2Fd33n5dQ8lWUE00s/" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <style>
        .checked {
            color: orange;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">
                <h3 class="card-title">Crayon en bois</h3>
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
                    <small>#245786654</small>
                    <span class="badge badge-success" style="font-size: 15px;">Fourniture de bureau</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <div class="media">
                    <div class="media-left">
                        <img class="media-object" src="stylo-plume.jpg" alt="produit ...." style="max-width: 35rem; min-width: 35rem;">
                    </div>
                    <div class="media-body">
                        <p>
                            <h1 id="spPrix">5,00$</h1>
                            <span><span class="font-weight-bold">Vendu par:</span> <a href="#">Bureau en gros</a></span><br />
                            <span class="fa fa-star checked"></span>
                            <span class="fa fa-star checked"></span>
                            <span class="fa fa-star checked"></span>
                            <span class="fa fa-star checked"></span>
                            <span class="fa fa-star"></span><br />
                        </p>
                        <hr>
                        <p>
                            <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-success">Ajouter au panier <span class="fas fa-shopping-cart"></span></button>
                            <span id="spQqt"><span class="font-weight-bold">&nbsp;&nbsp;Quantité restant:</span> 5</span>
                        </p>
                        <hr>
                        <p class="font-weight-bold">Description:</p>
                        <p>Plume à l'encre de longue durée pour une utilisation quotidienne. La coque en banbou est fabriquée avec des matériaux éco-responsable. Attention à ne pas consommer l'encre et tenir loin des enfants de moins de 3 ans. </p>
                        <p>
                            <span class="font-weight-bold">Poids:</span><span> 1 lb</span><br />
                            <span><span class="font-weight-bold">En vente depuis:</span> 24-01-2019</span>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
